Title: [ANN][ONGOING ICO!] 🔹 MeeTip 🔹 CONNECTING PLACES OF ENCOUNTERS 👥
Body: Forgive me my ignorance, trying to pull it together... How would I be able to located my friends in order to offer them drink through MeeTip? Does it mean they have to run the app, too, and allow the app to have access to their current location? What about some privacy?

Author: Meetip
Title: [ANN][ONGOING ICO!] 🔹 MeeTip 🔹 CONNECTING PLACES OF ENCOUNTERS 👥
Body: Indeed, your friends must be users of the app and allow the location.  By logging into the app, you will have access to the location of your Facebook friends when they indicate to be in an establishment. Therefore, privacy is respected, the geolocation is not constant but operates only when a person voluntarily indicates to be in an establishment in order to take advantage of all functionalities. The interest also lies in proximity meetings. Thus, geolocation is important to interact with people around you. Note that you retain the option "I don't want to be located".  It is also good to know that we will use the Blockchain Bigchain DB for data decentralization. We will be the first proximity meetings mobile app not to store on a centralized server the personal and intimate information (first name, sexual and religious orientation ...) of the user.  You can watch this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4aCcjmY_aOI   which details each feature, including how to indicate your presence in an establishment (1min19).

Author: Meetip
Title: [ANN][ONGOING ICO!] 🔹 MeeTip 🔹 CONNECTING PLACES OF ENCOUNTERS 👥
Body: To clarify this point, it is true that a year ago we were not ready to give up our project which started to show interest. This was one of the first big proposals we had, we did not want to act hastily and to regret later. Especially since it is not only about the financial side. There is a soul, there is a story and especially a team attached to this project. Bringing it to fruition by ourselves is part of a strong will from us. That's why today we have made the choice to continue our ICO without external influence. With all respect and caution, we will consider these offers later.

Author: bribed
Title: [ANN][ONGOING ICO!] 🔹 MeeTip 🔹 CONNECTING PLACES OF ENCOUNTERS 👥
Body: I dont really get this. Maybe its because where I live we still buy drinks from the counter or talk to a waitress and then tip face to face... So what is this coin all about? Dont get me wrong, Im not hating here, but I really think some parts of life should still be "smartphone free". Just my opinion. Please enlight me if this is about way more than just tipping via an app.

Author: OutMySphere
Title: [ANN][ONGOING ICO!] 🔹 MeeTip 🔹 CONNECTING PLACES OF ENCOUNTERS 👥
Body: We can answer you in 3 ways.  First of all with regard to the actual features, what you are saying are some possibilities offered by the application but it goes further. For the beverages orders, it is not simply to avoid ordering at the counter, it can nevertheless be a time saver, but it is mainly to propose the order in a decentralized way. Since you can visualize who is in a bar, and especially where your Facebook friends are, you will be able to offer a drink to whatever place you are located respectively. If your friend is in a bar in New York and you live in France, there is no limit. For the Tip feature, again it's not just about tipping through the app only to the waiter you have in front of you. Employees present using the app will all be able to receive a tip, ie not only the waiter but also the people you never see, the cooks for example. You will be able to choose any employee. In addition, the app also provides details about the crowd in real time in all places to our users.  In a second time, we agree with you that human contact will always be better than the virtual side. However, society is evolving and the digital revolution is creating new needs. Our app offers a service that responds to a request. You can offer a drink to a stranger directly, it will help shy people for example. The goal is to use the application as an icebreaker in your social relations. Also, today you have the opportunity to buy on the Internet like buying a product in a real shop. To make a long story short, these are adaptations.  Finally, you have to understand that we put forward this cryptocurrency in the context of our own application. But it will also be used in other dating applications in the future when partenerships will be developped.  We thank you for your question

Author: Meetip
Title: [ANN][ONGOING ICO!] 🔹 MeeTip 🔹 CONNECTING PLACES OF ENCOUNTERS 👥
Body: As a user, this cryptocurrency will allow to take advantage of the Drink and Tip functionalities.  As an investor, the number of MeeTip tokens is limited to 30,000,000 and no further tokens could be created due to the strict laws of smart-contracts. All tokens sold during the pre-ICO and main ICO will be the only MeeTip ever in circulation. Once OutMySphere is complete and integrates MeeTip tokens, the demand of MeeTip will increase, as more people demand it as a form of payment for drinks and tips. Indeed, MeeTip cryptocurrency aims at being the reference cryptocurrency of meetings i.e a mean of payment in bars, restaurants, cafes ... What you should understand is that this cryptocurrency will be used in other mobile app depending on our partnerships. To give you an idea, we have already had contacts with the Match Group (Tinder, Meetic), which suggests promising prospects.  Then, a total of 15% of all MTIP in circulation will be purchased back by our company during the first 24 hours on first exchange to help MeeTip entering a bullish trend. If the bullish trend sticks, the price of MeeTip should steadily increase.  Everything has been organized to guarantee the investments of our investors.  Let us know if you have any further questions and we will be more than happy to reply more precisely.

Author: OutMySphere
Title: [ANN][ONGOING ICO!] 🔹 MeeTip 🔹 CONNECTING PLACES OF ENCOUNTERS 👥
Body: Hello,  It is a process which tends to develop but which remains hardly discernible. We summarize our project by decentralizing order and payment processes, but we must keep in mind all the features to appreciate its value. Indeed, the interest of our application does not lie in the mere fact of ordering drinks. It also allows to interact with people in the same bar via encrypted messaging, to know the name and the sentimental status of unknown people until then, to offer a drink to people you like and to your friends wherever they are. It is much more enjoyable to receive a free drink from one of your friend at the other end of the world, it can put you in a good mood when you see people are thinking about you. More than just sending them money, which loses all its charm.  You will be also able to tip every employee and not only the waiter. As you are able to view people in the same place, you will see every single employee using the app i.e the barman, the cook, you will have a wider choice and really have the opportunity to thank each person. It will be interesting in countries, for instance in France, inasmuch as tip is not included in bill. It can really encourage tipping in countries where it is not a common practise.  In addition, the application mainly allows to know the crowd in real time in all the establishments and to be able to choose the place where to spend your evening according to targeted criteria (very frequented or rather peaceful place).  Therefore, the purpose of the app is to optimize your outings, meetings and social relationships by creating interactions. We really want to break with dating applications that sometimes lead to unhealthy trends, which ultimately degrade the meeting and the quality of social relationships.  This system will also be advantageous to establishments owners. They can take advantage of our app and not have to create their own system, it is  time and money saving. In addition, they will profit from two proposed cocktails especially created for our features. From a marketing view, it can lead to attract new customers.  The idea is to create a community and distinctive sign around our project in order to promote meetings in all ways.  Finally, we will be the first proximity meeting mobile app to use the technology of the blockchain and not to store on a centralized server the personal and intimate information of the user such as his first name, sexual and religious orientation and many others.  The Ethereum and BigchainDB blockchains will enable to manage interactions between people within these establishments.

Title: [ANN][ONGOING ICO!] 🔹 MeeTip 🔹 CONNECTING PLACES OF ENCOUNTERS 👥
Body: This case will be rare because the person is free to accept or refuse the drink before the transaction is approved. One can legitimately guess that if she accepts, it would be logical for her to take the drink. On the other hand, if for any technical reason she can't take the drink, a notification is then sent to the person who offered it, so that she can recover and offer it herself.

Title: [ANN][ONGOING ICO!] 🔹 MeeTip 🔹 CONNECTING PLACES OF ENCOUNTERS 👥
Body: To answer you, neither one!  We can not talk about partnership as it would certainly be difficult for us to reach an agreement with them. In all transparency, this is what we felt at the first discussion with one of their interlocutors. Our business conduct proved to be too different for that. And absolutely no resentment from us. Simply, we are not in phase with the way that meetings can be proposed in this application. We want to optimize social relations and give them a little authenticity. We do not want to stop at the superficial side of the meetings. Our goal is primarily to focus on quality meetings. We choose quality rather than quantity. But also to offer much more than meeting with our other features. All the functionalities have to be taken as a whole to appreciate the project.
